page.title: 15Miss Woodcock
page.content: Miss Woodcock is the{churchwarden}of {Hewelsfield church.}She has been a {churchwarden for 16 years.}She carries her {father's churchwarden staff.} Miss Woodcock helps to make the{parish {magazine}in the vestry of the church every month with a duplicating machine.She has lived in Hewelsfield for{50 years.}There is an {old sunday {school}by the church which is about { {135 years old.}Miss Woodcock goes to church every Sunday.She enjoys the garden and the countryside.Her hobbies are {lace making,}music and gardening.She has helped us a lot with our Domesday Project.
